root: ^How? Just how?? You're not supposed to be getting through my minions!!!
^We're just doing what comes naturally, to be honest.
^Wha- What the heck do you mean?? How many times have you done this before?
^I don't know, but it feels like a déjà vu to me.
^Yeah. We once fought back against a wandering pi-thon. She was actually pretty acute, once you got to know her.
^You think you are so skillful, do you? Well have a taste of this!!
